Summary: This sub-phase investigates whether MemPalace-style wake-up layering is worth prototyping only as a bounded read model or formatter on top of `session_bootstrap` and related recovery surfaces. It studies token budgets, recovery quality, and duplication risk. It does not approve a new wake-up command or storage model.
